                    <h2>Dissolved Oxygen</h2>
                    <h3>Dissolved Oxygen concentrations (mg/L) in Abu Dabhi Emirate waters.</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Dissolved Oxygen (DO) (oxygen concentration of marine water) levels met recommended water quality standards for Abu Dhabi's marine environment during the first quarter of 2013. All stations were above the recommended minimum threshold of 4mg/L. Station 2 had the lowest DO average for the quarter (4.1mg/L). Marine water quality stations near ports and marinas had the lowest DO concentrations for the quarter, but all were above the recommended minimun.</p>
                <img src="/images/visualisations/05.png" alt="visualisation 5">
            </section>
